Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.49,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.21,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:22.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.43,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:34.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Something like this? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. A little bit more this way, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have improved a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans for this coming weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This coming weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...the senior members and I are going to my vacation home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We will plan and prepare for my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward to your birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shinobu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are... some things for the party you could help me prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you two come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Gladly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some juice, Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a promise to Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We said we'd all go somewhere together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped! That was a request from Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we've already been given two round-trip tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who promised Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about it! I'll go somewhere with Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That promise to Tomoko-san was only in case nothing else happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that settles that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we're already on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already given her such a hard time! Poor Tomoko. Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Miya-sama asked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you just say "Sorry!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Founder's Day is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have to spend it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...just as I promised: guidebooks, scheduling, pricing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd taken care of all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A souvenir, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A souvenir! Whether I ever speak to you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...depends upon the souvenir you bring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course, I'll pay for the souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can guess, my dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...we are on our way to Miya-sama's vacation home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,22. A Summer's Serenade
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to have you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have two more joining us. Please see to their needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Take the luggage out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Minako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, can you take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless, forgetting such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It slipped my mind... I was so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please see to our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be spending my time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will. Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer's day is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Minako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Minako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You made another mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you got the watch and the pencil case reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single detail in that room must remain unchanged!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry. I'll put them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already corrected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... it's wonderful! It's like a Chateau on the Rhine River!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind to think of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,First year members have never been invited here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You should feel very honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a walk. You can see her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, perhaps I should show you what we have for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This sun room will be your work room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our assignment was to prepare all the invitations
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...for Miya-sama birthday party the following week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There were about 300 names, filling two address books.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I ever wondered if it could be finished in a single weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A trip with Tomoko might have been better, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san, look! The lake is shimmering!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We should after coming all the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A violin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Softly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a melancholy cry for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...the music gently penetrated the deep woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For whom was she crying out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama, proud Fukiko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...crying for help, but to whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As if suffering the unbearable pain of tragic love...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...love?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Her love?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But... who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was the coffee I had with dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Mariko-san was sleeping soundly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...somehow tonight I was unable to fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been past one o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a splash of water nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was definitely Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The trail of droplets led upward,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...past Miya-sama's bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of a long hallway, after a couple of turns,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...I heard her voice again from behind the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I compare thee to a summer's day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Thou art more lovely and more temperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rough winds do shake the darling buds of May,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and summer's lease hath all too short a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometime hot the eye of heaven shines, oft his gold complexion dims,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair from fair sometime declines, by nature's changing course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But thy eternal summer shall not fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor shall Death brag,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,..thou wanderest in his Shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When in eternal lines to time thou growest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In eternal lines to time thou growest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! Where've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...well... the bathroom. The downstairs one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shock! Waking up and finding myself alone in bed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me alone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care for more coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Her smile is elegant, quiet, and calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As if nothing at all had happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama appears no different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that voice remains with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice from that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...a voice which seemed torn from her deepest heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... they're so pretentious. Playing badminton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The last train is at 8, tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't finish, we'll have to take it home with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, how many do you have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... about 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... you're lucky! I have at least 120!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought something cool to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose room is that, on the 3rd floor, at the very end of the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the "sealed chamber".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The "sealed chamber"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what we call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That room was Fukiko-sama's, until she turned 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been left exactly as it was then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As it was? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Minako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking about family matters to our guests is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I sincerely apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Igarasi-san! Igarasi-san, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get rid of Minako-san immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not suitable to serve the Ichinomiya family as a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that reason enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But can't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but I only asked her about the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama! Please wait, Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me! I asked her about that room. It's not her fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be concerned. No need to defend her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't entirely over what happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't involved in this. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm a born gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be fired so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see what being a maid was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my hobby, to change jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm living with my parents in a neighboring town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as kind as you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind people draw me out like that. I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,About the "sealed chamber"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can go inside except Fukiko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even other family members.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day before Fukiko-sama arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sent in to clean the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama would scold me mercilessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...if there was even the slightest change in a doll's location!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is exactly as it was 6 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When Miya-sama was 12 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye. Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, this lake is very dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in, Nanako-san. It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanako-san. I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to swim with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Nanako-san, are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you fell in a swimming pool, and swallowed some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tale 50 of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to write you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.55,0:23:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't share today's experiences with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.75,0:23:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Never, as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:14.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:19.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:25.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:37.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:42.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:50.45,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.72,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.56,0:25:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At her 18th birthday party,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.81,0:25:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste plays the violin in Fukiko's honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.04,0:25:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...attempting to please her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.42,0:25:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of Saint-Juste's efforts come to naught,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when Fukiko reacts unexpectedly...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.65,0:25:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Forbidden Gift
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.58,0:25:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
